==現今狀況==

===北約===

北約部隊對於一位前進空中管制員必須要有的資格與經驗皆定義於{{Link-en|北約標準化協議|Standardization Agreement}}（STANAG）中。前進空中管制員可以是地面部隊{{Link-en|火力支援小組|Fire Support Team}}或是[[战术空军管制组|戰術空中管制組]]（'''T'''actical '''A'''ir '''C'''ontrol '''P'''arty，TACP）的一員，也可由飛機搭載（FAC-A)或是直升機搭載（ABFAC）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mod.uk/NR/rdonlyres/4463968B-8061-4E75-BDC3-05074EFA8AFF/0/20071218_ijwp3_30_U_DCDCIMAPPS.pdf|title=Joint Air Operations Interim Joint warfare Publication 3-30|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=MoD|pages=4–5|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110608001520/http://www.mod.uk/NR/rdonlyres/4463968B-8061-4E75-BDC3-05074EFA8AFF/0/20071218_ijwp3_30_U_DCDCIMAPPS.pdf|archivedate=2011年6月8日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>[[美军|美軍]]自2003年以後便改稱地面版的前進空中管制員為[[聯合終端攻擊管制員|聯合終端攻擊管制員]]（'''J'''oint '''T'''erminal '''A'''ttack '''C'''ontrollers，JTAC）。<ref name=wyatt>Caroline Wyatt, 14 February 2009, "Training the RAF's eyes and ears", ''BBC NEWS'' [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/7887892.stm] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/7887892.stm |date=20160307090953 }} Retrieved 3 October 2015.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://sill-www.army.mil/FAMAG/1968/JAN_1968/JAN_1968_PAGES_59_68.pdf|title=Close air Support and the Forward Observer|author=Maj J Stallings|work=Tactics Combined Arms Dep USAAMS|date=Jan 1968|accessdate=2017-01-03|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907161436/https://sill-www.army.mil/FAMAG/1968/JAN_1968/JAN_1968_PAGES_59_68.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[北大西洋公约组织|北約]]一直致力於增加空地行動的安全性，並減低友軍誤擊的風險。為了使不同的北約單位能一同順利合作，{{Link-en|北約標準化辦公室|NATO Standardization Office}}與{{Link-en|聯合空中力量能力中心|Joint Air Power Competence Centre}}一同制定了前進空中管制的相關流程與定義，並撰寫在第3797{{Link-en|標準化協定中|Standardization Agreement}}《前進空中管制員的基礎資格》(Minimum Qualifications for Forward Air Controllers)。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://aero-defense.ihs.com/document/abstract/FJYQJBAAAAAAAAAA|title=NATO STANAG 3797 MINIMUM QUALIFICATIONS FOR FORWARD AIR CONTROLLERS & LASER OPERATORS IN SUPPORT OF FORWARD AIR CONTROLLERS|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=NATO|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090829190451/http://aero-defense.ihs.com/document/abstract/FJYQJBAAAAAAAAAA|archivedate=2009年8月29日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>北約的前進空中管制員受訓後可以呼叫、計劃、簡報、執行中低空、高空密接空中支援的能力，同時也會學習像是[[電子作戰|電子作戰]]、[[壓制敵方防空任務|壓制敵方防空任務]]、敵軍防空能力、空中指揮與管制、攻擊方法、戰術與{{Link-en|武器使用|Weaponeering}}等專業知識。<ref>[http://www.raf.mod.uk/idtraf/courses/4704.cfm] {{Wayback|url=http://www.raf.mod.uk/idtraf/courses/4704.cfm |date=20160303190353 }} Anonymous, "Forward Air Controllers (FAC) - 4704", INTERNATIONAL DEFENCE TRAINING, Royal Air Force, publication date unknown, unpaginated. Retrieved 4 October 2015.</ref>

===英軍===

英軍的前進空中管制員在{{Link-en|聯合前進空中管制員訓練與標準化中心|Joint Forward Air Controller Training and Standards Unit}}（'''J'''oint '''F'''orward Air '''C'''ontroller '''T'''raining and '''S'''tandards '''U'''nit，JFACTSU）中進行訓練。<ref name=wyatt/>英軍根據行動經驗把前進空中管制員放進{{Link-en|火力支援小組|Fire Support Team}}中，使他們也能像是[[战术空军管制组|戰術空中管制組]]一樣來指揮大範圍的火力支援任務。<ref>[http://www.army.mod.uk/artillery/24139.aspx] {{Wayback|url=http://www.army.mod.uk/artillery/24139.aspx |date=20160701133541 }}, Anonymous, "Join as a Soldier", Ministry of Defence. Retrieved 4 October 2015.</ref>前進空中管制員的人可以是來自[[英國皇家海軍陸戰隊|皇家海軍陸戰隊]]（也有的是{{Link-en|皇家海軍陸戰後備隊|Royal Marines Reserve}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.royalnavy.mod.uk/server/show/nav.2984 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-05-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070610135402/http://www.royalnavy.mod.uk/server/show/nav.2984 |archivedate=2007-06-10 }}, Anonymous, "Specialist Qualification", Ministry of Defence Archived 10 June 2007 at the Wayback Machine.</ref>或{{Link-en|英國皇家空軍地面團|RAF Regiment|皇家空軍地面團}}<ref>[http://www.raf.mod.uk/rafregiment/careers/fac.cfm] {{Wayback|url=http://www.raf.mod.uk/rafregiment/careers/fac.cfm |date=20160616235003 }}, Anonymous, "The RAF Regiment - Experiences of a Forward Air Controller". Raf.mod.uk Retrieved 28 April 2013.</ref>戰術空中管制組的人員。{{Link-en|陸軍航空兵|Army Air Corps (United Kingdom)}}也有提供機載版的前進空中管制員。<ref name=":0" />

===美國海軍陸戰隊===

當在佈署部隊時，每個海軍陸戰連都會配屬1位前進空中管制員或是[[聯合終端攻擊管制員|聯合終端攻擊管制員]]。

===阿富汗國民軍===

[[阿富汗國民軍|阿富汗國民軍]]依靠盟友來提高並維持他們前進空中管制員與聯合火力管制官（'''J'''oint '''F'''ires '''O'''fficer，JFO）的水平。<ref>[http://tribune-intl.com/asutralian-excels-in-afghan-army-advisory-role/] {{Wayback|url=http://tribune-intl.com/asutralian-excels-in-afghan-army-advisory-role/ |date=20160403142439 }} Editor. "Australian excels in Afghan Army advisory role". Tribune International (Australia), 18 October 2014. Retrieved 4 October 2014.</ref>藉由澳洲聯合火力管制官的協助，阿富汗成功建立出戰術空中協調員來執行這些任務。<ref>Anonymous. "Cooper Dale makes a difference in Afghanistan". ''South Coast Register'' 16 September 2014. [http://www.southcoastregister.com.au/story/2563708/meanwhile-in-afghanistan/] {{Wayback|url=http://www.southcoastregister.com.au/story/2563708/meanwhile-in-afghanistan/ |date=20160402042011 }} Retrieved 4 October 2015.</ref>

